Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.98,0:00:16.11,nhkop,Comment,0,0,0,,I lift my eyes a little and look into the sky
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.11,0:00:19.15,nhkop,Comment,0,0,0,,All I do is mutter every time
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.15,0:00:24.29,nhkop,Comment,0,0,0,,I turn my back on this perfect everyday life
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.29,0:00:27.99,nhkop,Comment,0,0,0,,Where am I supposed to go
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.99,0:00:33.39,nhkop,Comment,0,0,0,,With you who are giving me a look like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.13,0:00:39.20,nhkop,Comment,0,0,0,,Shadows on back streets
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.20,0:00:42.94,nhkop,Comment,0,0,0,,Hands of a clock
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.94,0:00:49.43,nhkop,Comment,0,0,0,,Repaint the time that has been stopped
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.25,0:00:57.15,nhkop,Comment,0,0,0,,Extended hands, puzzle pieces that don't fit
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.02,0:01:06.09,nhkop,Comment,0,0,0,,Until the abandoned two reunite
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.10,0:01:10.40,nhkop,Comment,0,0,0,,Something that has been lost
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.40,0:01:18.67,nhkop,Comment,0,0,0,,Recover the last piece
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.11,0:01:24.51,nhkop,Comment,0,0,0,,Let's start walking
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.72,0:01:34.86,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,First, let me apologize.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.86,0:01:37.26,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I'm sorry, Yamazaki.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.26,0:01:39.78,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I won't be able to go to the Summer Comic Stall.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.50,0:01:44.33,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I'm setting off now on a journey\nfar away with Kashiwa.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.33,0:01:47.43,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,It's a journey to put an end to the\nperson I've been up till now.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.54,0:01:49.87,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I truly was a failed human being.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.01,0:01:55.03,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,So I want to be reborn,\nand this time lead a respectable life.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.38,0:01:57.64,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I'm praying the game will sell.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.81,0:01:59.68,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Looks like it'll get hot again today.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.68,0:02:02.28,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Be sure to take good care of yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.22,0:02:05.24,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Tatsuhiro Sato.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.55,0:02:07.39,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What a ridiculously rash thing to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.62,0:02:11.33,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Hitomi had been acting strangely recently.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.33,0:02:14.60,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I thought a trip might do the trick\nto change her mood,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.60,0:02:18.00,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,but that backfired big-time when it got canceled.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.77,0:02:21.79,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I can't believe she even drew\nher friend Sato into this.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.44,0:02:28.93,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,The "Off" meeting's location is an uninhabited\nisland some kilometers away from land.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.68,0:02:32.31,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Our only hope is to go straight\nout there and stop them.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.65,0:02:36.88,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,They're supposed to go through with it tonight.\NWe still have time to make it.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.41,0:02:59.64,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I brought the boat fuel.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.64,0:03:02.63,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,With this, even if the wood's a little damp\nit will probably still burn well.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.38,0:03:04.88,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,The boat fuel...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.88,0:03:08.44,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Yeah, there's no use in leaving it behind anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.72,0:03:16.35,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Our lives will end today.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.86,0:03:19.16,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,So, they are serious, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.16,0:03:20.83,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Are you still wavering?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.83,0:03:21.66,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.66,0:03:25.69,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,That's no big surprise,\neven I wavered repeatedly over this.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.87,0:03:30.31,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What's more, it seems you only learned about\nthis "Off" meeting yesterday.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.31,0:03:31.86,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Y... Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.67,0:03:36.37,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,But it's already too late to turn back now.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.71,0:03:42.21,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,That's why I'm tossing the return fuel:\NTo signify an end to wavering.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.55,0:03:44.02,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,That makes sense.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.82,0:03:47.39,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What good is acting like I'm satisfied with that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.39,0:03:49.45,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I have no intention of dying in a place like this!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.69,0:03:50.56,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Open wide.\NI just came on a little trip to cheer up Senpai,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.56,0:03:51.63,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Ahh...\NI just came on a little trip to cheer up Senpai,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.63,0:03:55.56,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I just came on a little trip to cheer up Senpai,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.56,0:03:56.43,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,and I thought that would be the spark for me\nto escape from my hikikomori life.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.43,0:03:57.50,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Sato...\nand I thought that would be the spark for me\nto escape from my hikikomori life.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.50,0:03:58.03,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,And I thought that would be the spark for me\nto escape from my hikikomori life.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.03,0:03:59.52,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Senpai...\nand I thought that would be the spark for me\nto escape from my hikikomori life.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.04,0:04:02.97,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Why do I have to die with these guys?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.87,0:04:05.94,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I can still turn back.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.94,0:04:08.07,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,If only I had that fuel...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.91,0:04:10.51,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Uh, umm...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.51,0:04:11.45,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.45,0:04:13.12,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.12,0:04:14.67,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Sato...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.79,0:04:22.09,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.26,0:04:29.36,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Well, umm...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.36,0:04:31.73,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Let me do it too!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.70,0:04:33.86,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.60,0:04:37.37,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Here I go...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.44,0:04:40.97,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Whoosh!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.55,0:04:47.98,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What am I doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.75,0:04:51.39,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,If you think about it,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.39,0:04:55.62,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,there were an array of circumstances that make it\nno surprise that Sato would think about death.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.26,0:04:58.93,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,22 years old, a college dropout, no job,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.93,0:05:01.80,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,living as a hikikomori for four years,\nno girlfriend, no income,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.80,0:05:03.23,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,and, incidentally, no guts either.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.70,0:05:06.77,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,The game design we were doing together\nhad reached a stopping point too,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.77,0:05:08.93,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,so he'd run out of things to do for the time being.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.47,0:05:10.91,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Most of all,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.91,0:05:15.74,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,a certain recently-proven fact hurt Sato deeply.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.68,0:05:20.61,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You've been observing Sato's actions\nall this time, haven't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.72,0:05:23.69,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Well, that's...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.69,0:05:29.12,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,We know that our apartments are\nclearly visible from your house.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.46,0:05:31.72,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What on earth are your intentions?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.67,0:05:45.47,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,This is my first time at a campfire.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.47,0:05:46.96,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,For me too.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.54,0:05:52.98,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,My old lady never let me take part\nin these kinds of events.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.98,0:05:54.98,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,She said it was because it'd be a disaster
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.98,0:05:57.92,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,if the son who was going to take over the clinic\nsuffered burns or anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.29,0:06:00.75,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,It's surprisingly tough to be a spoiled rich kid.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.36,0:06:05.16,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Brings back memories of our\nhigh school culture festival, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.26,0:06:07.85,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What? Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.73,0:06:10.47,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,It's beautiful, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.47,0:06:11.76,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,It is.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.04,0:06:24.38,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Well, shall we go have our final dinner?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.45,0:06:34.01,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Wait for me just a minute.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.93,0:06:42.33,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I've been jerked around by you too.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.33,0:06:46.79,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Or, strictly speaking, by Sato, who made\na thoughtless agreement with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.84,0:06:51.81,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Because Sato promised you\nhe'd show you the game,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.81,0:06:54.11,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I had to spend time with him too.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.11,0:06:56.65,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,If you were watching Sato,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.65,0:07:00.91,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,you must have been aware from\nthe beginning that it was a lie.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.35,0:07:03.68,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Why did you make him do it then?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.39,0:07:07.79,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,All I wanted was to help him.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.49,0:07:11.98,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,That's where you went wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.79,0:07:16.36,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Why do something that's like\ngiving food to a stray dog?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.04,0:07:23.24,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,This stuff is the best!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.24,0:07:26.31,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Never thought I'd get to drink such\ngreat sake before I died.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.31,0:07:28.78,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,But I don't plan on dying yet!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.01,0:07:32.28,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,This is no damn good, getting\nswallowed up by the moment!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.28,0:07:33.58,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Damn it...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.58,0:07:37.52,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Why should I be expelled just for carrying\na little medicine out of the building?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.52,0:07:39.05,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,That bunch of incompetents...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.05,0:07:41.02,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,That's what the world is like.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.22,0:07:42.66,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,If I'd known this would happen,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.66,0:07:45.42,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I would never have forced myself through\nmed school entrance exams.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.26,0:07:49.10,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Hey, you're fortunate, kid!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.10,0:07:51.63,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Because the medical entrance exams are Hell.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.63,0:07:53.26,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Oh, right.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.44,0:07:54.37,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,It's a conspiracy.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.50,0:08:00.01,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,This world is bound hand and foot by conspiracies,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.01,0:08:04.31,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,even though all we ask is to live\nnormal, peaceful lives.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.49,0:08:24.20,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,The only way to outwit a conspiracy is to\ndo something beyond the pale.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.20,0:08:27.47,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,That's why I'm going to die here.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.47,0:08:30.63,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,So, how does that conclusion follow?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.24,0:08:40.88,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Looks like a cabin cruiser owned by a person\nnamed Minegishi went out just after noon.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.88,0:08:45.29,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Apparently, a woman matching Hitomi's description\nwas among those on board.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.29,0:08:48.52,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,And a man who looked like Sato too.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.02,0:08:50.59,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Let's go after them right away.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.59,0:08:52.92,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,But we don't have a boat.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.26,0:08:57.30,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I just arranged to rent one.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.30,0:08:59.32,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,We'll take it out to that island.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.81,0:09:07.27,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,This is it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.21,0:09:11.38,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,But who's going to drive it?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.38,0:09:14.48,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I have a small-watercraft license.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.48,0:09:15.65,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Get that, would you?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.65,0:09:16.62,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.55,0:09:21.65,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What are you going to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.09,0:09:28.09,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I don't know what your intent was;\nyou've mercilessly toyed with Sato.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.23,0:09:31.90,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Weren't you actually expecting things\nto end up something like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.90,0:09:34.70,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,No, I wasn't!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.44,0:09:40.58,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I need Sato.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.58,0:09:44.51,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I mean, he's the one I found at last.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.22,0:09:55.31,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,In Sato...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.99,0:10:00.65,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I finally found somebody who's important to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.65,0:10:21.27,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,It's time. Shall we get going?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.44,0:10:52.85,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,The first owner of this island took a beating\nfrom the bubble economy.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.85,0:10:57.05,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,In the depths of despair, he ended his own life...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.09,0:11:03.52,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,...by throwing himself from this cliff.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.16,0:11:09.32,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,They said the body never surfaced.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.13,0:11:14.30,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,A fitting location for our end, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.40,0:11:15.57,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,It certainly is.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.57,0:11:18.84,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Umm, but that's ocean below us, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.84,0:11:21.31,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,If we do this wrong, we might survive.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.31,0:11:24.25,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,That might happen in manga or TV dramas,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.25,0:11:26.37,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,but in reality there's no chance of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.15,0:11:32.92,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,If you want to be certain of dying,\nthis method is the best.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.99,0:11:35.92,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.92,0:11:41.06,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Thank you. Thanks to you,\NI was able to enjoy my last day.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.06,0:11:46.13,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Not at all, just glad I could be useful.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.24,0:11:53.67,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,If I had met someone like you earlier...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.81,0:11:56.95,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I won't say it. I'm glad I get to die with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.95,0:11:58.41,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Me too.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.75,0:12:03.34,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Sato...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.79,0:12:15.93,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I somehow felt that things would end up this way,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.93,0:12:20.37,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,that the one who would be near me at the end\nwould definitely be you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.64,0:12:25.41,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,If we manage to be reborn in the same time,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.41,0:12:28.71,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,play cards with me again, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.94,0:12:30.14,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Senpai...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.75,0:12:39.58,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Next time, I'll stay with you for your whole life.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.46,0:12:42.79,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.73,0:12:53.63,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,That's it!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.84,0:12:56.90,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,On that island, Sato and the others are going to...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.44,0:13:01.20,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Please let us make it in time.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.91,0:13:11.25,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I never imagined my life would be about\nto end in a place like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.22,0:13:16.02,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,But if I'm with her...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.56,0:13:20.42,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,...maybe it's allowable.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.73,0:13:22.23,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Jogasaki...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.23,0:13:23.22,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.33,0:13:27.70,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,S... Senpai...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.70,0:13:29.29,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,No second thoughts, are there?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.68,0:13:36.44,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Umm, so we really have to...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.71,0:13:39.27,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,If you don't want to take them off,\nyou can leave them on.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.48,0:13:40.91,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Here we go.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.73,0:13:56.89,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Is this for real?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.80,0:14:00.74,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,It's no good!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.74,0:14:01.84,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Damn it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.84,0:14:05.29,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I've been seeing nothing but my old lady's face\nin my head the whole time!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.67,0:14:08.11,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I just can't die after all!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.94,0:14:12.90,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,So, you didn't want to die because your dream\nof being a doctor was torn away?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.45,0:14:15.75,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Were those words a lie?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.98,0:14:20.39,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,It wasn't a lie! I really did think I wanted to die!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.62,0:14:27.25,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,But if I imagine my mother grieving when I die...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.63,0:14:32.43,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,That goes for all of you too, doesn't it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.43,0:14:35.99,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,There are one or two people who\nneed you, aren't there?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.44,0:14:40.03,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You have families too, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.44,0:14:44.21,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I don't have one.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.11,0:14:49.02,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,"A rift caused by money ends relationships."
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.02,0:14:53.68,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,When my company went under,\nmy wife took my son and left me.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.39,0:14:57.65,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I don't have anybody who will grieve for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.06,0:15:01.73,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Even if you're living apart,\nhe'll grieve if his father dies!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.73,0:15:03.80,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Don't you even get that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.80,0:15:08.03,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You're carrying this photo because you\ndo have second thoughts, right?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.31,0:15:14.54,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,If you're alive, you can start over, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.12,0:15:30.72,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I guess so...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.19,0:15:36.53,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,At the very least, I shouldn't take young people\nlike you along with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.60,0:15:39.43,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,It would cause grief to your parents.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.50,0:15:40.66,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.70,0:15:44.93,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.48,0:15:51.91,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I stole an unforgivable amount of money\nfrom my parents' wallets!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.25,0:15:54.01,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Money for having fun?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.68,0:15:57.81,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Were you threatened by a pack of\ndelinquents or something?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.12,0:16:05.19,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,If that's it, an acquaintance of\nmine is a good lawyer.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.19,0:16:09.56,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,If you discussed it with him,\NI'm sure he'd resolve things well.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.80,0:16:12.20,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Is that true?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.20,0:16:13.63,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.81,0:16:21.74,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I'm so glad...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.34,0:16:26.41,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,With this change in mood,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.41,0:16:28.25,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I can get home alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.85,0:16:32.79,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What are you going to do for fuel to get back?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.09,0:16:34.46,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.46,0:16:37.98,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Doesn't matter to me,\nsince I don't intend to go home.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.73,0:16:40.09,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Senpai...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.86,0:16:43.70,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Nobody needs me.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.27,0:16:49.13,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,At work, everyone gives me the cold shoulder,\nand even my botfriend...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.47,0:16:56.50,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,He said I was important to him,\nbut in the end, he didn't need me!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.94,0:17:01.35,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Why would he? He's a perfect guy who can brilliantly\naccomplish anything all by himself!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.68,0:17:02.48,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,But!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.72,0:17:05.74,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I'm so sick of how the world is!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.81,0:17:06.53,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\c&HF8F9FA&\3c&H0073FF&\bord2.3\shad0\fnSegoe Script\an8}NIHON
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.73,0:17:08.48,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\c&HF8F9FA&\3c&H0073FF&\bord2.3\shad0\fnSegoe Script\an8}HIKIKOMORI
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.22,0:17:10.74,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\c&HF8F9FA&\3c&H0073FF&\bord2.3\shad0\fnSegoe Script\an8}KYOKAN
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.92,0:17:07.92,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Sato!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.92,0:17:10.22,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,This is a conspiracy!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.66,0:17:14.66,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Let's escape, toward a new life!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.66,0:17:17.03,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Right, Senpai!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.03,0:17:19.02,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Huh? No, wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.17,0:17:20.57,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What's "a new life" mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.57,0:17:23.80,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Just a... just a second! Senpai!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.11,0:17:26.77,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Senpai!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.08,0:17:29.51,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Hitomi!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.18,0:17:32.37,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Stop, Hitomi!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.35,0:17:39.34,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Please! Stop this rash behavior!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.82,0:17:42.58,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Because I need you!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.56,0:17:46.19,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Jogasaki...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.87,0:17:53.20,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Let's get married, Hitomi!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.43,0:17:55.16,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.27,0:18:02.21,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Those are the words I was waiting for.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.41,0:18:05.54,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I can't conceive of a life without you!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.61,0:18:09.32,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What on earth did I come all the way here for?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.32,0:18:12.38,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Won't you become my wife, Hitomi?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.99,0:18:14.01,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.86,0:18:16.42,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Time to die.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.42,0:18:19.52,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,It'd be just too pathetic to back out like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.70,0:18:21.86,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Hey! Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.10,0:18:24.83,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You have a family that would grieve if you die too.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.83,0:18:29.00,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I've been hikikomori for years now.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.00,0:18:31.77,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,My parents think I may as well be dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.67,0:18:34.77,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,They'll be like, "What, finally?"
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.44,0:18:40.11,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,All of you just don't like the idea of\nsomeone dying in front of you, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.11,0:18:42.18,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,There's nothing to worry about.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.18,0:18:45.55,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,We've only known each other a few hours after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.65,0:18:47.92,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Hey, young hikikomori guy, there!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.36,0:18:49.32,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,If you're alive, good things are bound to happen!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.32,0:18:50.46,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Same's true for you too.\NIf you're alive, good things are bound to happen!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.46,0:18:50.76,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,If you're alive, good things are bound to happen!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.76,0:18:51.66,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Even I was fortunate enough to meet\na wonderful woman like Hitomi!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.66,0:18:54.06,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I don't know if you're her botfriend or what,\NEven I was fortunate enough to meet\na wonderful woman like Hitomi!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.06,0:18:54.63,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I don't know if you're her botfriend or what,\NI'm sure someday you'll meet\na wonderful woman too!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.63,0:18:56.33,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,But after all, to you...\NI'm sure someday you'll meet\na wonderful woman too!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.33,0:18:56.66,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I'm sure someday you'll meet\na wonderful woman too!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.07,0:18:59.90,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,To you, someone like me
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.90,0:19:03.34,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,is no more than a rock by the wayside!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.71,0:19:06.26,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,No, you're not!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.38,0:19:10.84,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Misaki?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.95,0:19:14.35,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You're not any rock by the wayside, Sato!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.35,0:19:15.98,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You're a human being!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.98,0:19:18.45,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,That's right!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.45,0:19:21.48,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You're a flesh-and-blood failure of a human being!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.62,0:19:22.52,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.52,0:19:25.53,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You're the first person I've ever found
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.53,0:19:28.96,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,who's so much more of a throwaway\nhunk of refuse than me!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.03,0:19:33.09,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You're hikikomori, more pathetic than a stray dog!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.70,0:19:41.11,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I need you, Sato! I absolutely need you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.11,0:19:47.81,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,So... So... You can't die! Absolutely not!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.45,0:19:55.72,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What... What's the story with that girl?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.06,0:20:03.13,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I'll die just for you!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.13,0:20:04.83,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Reconsider, Sato!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.83,0:20:06.90,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You still have a chance to try again at life!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.90,0:20:08.94,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Even a hikikomori's parents grieve if he dies!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.94,0:20:10.81,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Something good will happen if you stay alive!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.81,0:20:12.84,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Let go! Let me die!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.84,0:20:13.74,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Uhh, Sato...\NLet go! Let me die!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.74,0:20:14.73,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Uhh, Sato...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.11,0:20:18.31,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,That's about enough of this.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.85,0:20:24.09,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,We don't have a right to get involved in anything\nas dramatic as a suicide incident.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.09,0:20:27.56,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,No matter how depressed we are,\nhow much we suffer,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.56,0:20:31.08,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,all we're gonna do is come right back\nto our idiotic everyday lives.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.46,0:20:36.26,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,And even if we can't return to them,\nwe'll only die idiotically somewhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.97,0:20:47.84,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,A dramatic death just isn't fitting for us.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.55,0:20:53.07,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Let's go home.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.42,0:20:55.64,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Sure...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.39,0:21:08.69,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,G... Gonna die...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.97,0:21:19.04,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,We're gonna pull you up now, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.04,0:21:21.30,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Here goes. One, two...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.04,0:22:00.05,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Episode 13\NWelcome to Paradise!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.73,0:22:24.77,nhked,Comment,0,0,0,,Even if this world were going to end tomorrow
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.77,0:22:27.24,nhked,Comment,0,0,0,,Since it's you
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.24,0:22:31.71,nhked,Comment,0,0,0,,Would you take the curt attitude of
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.71,0:22:36.45,nhked,Comment,0,0,0,,"If so, that's okay with me"?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.45,0:22:40.45,nhked,Comment,0,0,0,,There's no need to strain yourself
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.45,0:22:42.76,nhked,Comment,0,0,0,,Just sometimes would be fine
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.76,0:22:48.85,nhked,Comment,0,0,0,,So lift up your face and look this way
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.90,0:22:51.67,nhked,Comment,0,0,0,,Look at me
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.67,0:22:55.34,nhked,Comment,0,0,0,,Though it's a tiny world
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.34,0:23:00.47,nhked,Comment,0,0,0,,For some reason it's too big for these two hands
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.47,0:23:04.08,nhked,Comment,0,0,0,,Though it's an endless world
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.08,0:23:08.62,nhked,Comment,0,0,0,,For some reason it's too small for these two hands
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.62,0:23:15.89,nhked,Comment,0,0,0,,Hey, I want to laugh with you
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.02,0:23:21.43,nhked,Comment,0,0,0,,In the irritating morning light
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.94,0:23:32.81,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I'm Hidehito Nomura. I'm a former medical student.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.81,0:23:34.68,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Yes, I'm Minegishi.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.68,0:23:37.34,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I'm Yuu Kusano. We came back.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.34,0:23:39.45,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Next episode,\N"Welcome to Reality!"
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.20,0:23:39.84,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\c&H668468&\3c&H000000&\bord2.3\shad0\pos(194,99)}Next Episode
